WEBVTT

00:03.421 --> 00:05.055
50 pounds down.

00:05.056 --> 00:08.157
It's been ten years since I've
been able to slip into these.

00:08.159 --> 00:10.861
I'm so proud of you. Maybe-maybe
hop a little. Okay, okay.

00:10.862 --> 00:13.297
I'll hop, you pull. Ready?
Yeah, yeah.

00:13.298 --> 00:15.565
(grunting)

00:15.566 --> 00:18.235
Yeah!

00:18.236 --> 00:21.738
There he is.
Hello, sexy.

00:21.739 --> 00:22.939
Hold on. We're not
out of the woods yet.

00:22.940 --> 00:24.207
I still got to zip.
Ooh, ooh!

00:24.208 --> 00:26.043
Lay on the bed.
I'll grab some pliers.

00:26.044 --> 00:27.377
Wait.

00:27.378 --> 00:29.212
Yeah!

00:29.213 --> 00:30.681
(imitating Rocky):
Ain't gonna be no rematch.

00:30.682 --> 00:32.883
Ain't gonna be no rematch!

00:32.884 --> 00:35.619
Oh. I bought these a decade ago

00:35.620 --> 00:37.621
after a both-ends stomach flu.

00:37.622 --> 00:40.157
It nearly killed me,
but I never looked better.

00:40.158 --> 00:41.758
Until now.

00:41.759 --> 00:43.994
You know, it's not everybody
that can wear their flu pants.

00:43.995 --> 00:46.163
And you did it the hard way.
Yep.

00:46.164 --> 00:48.231
Diet and exercise.
I did more of the things I hate

00:48.232 --> 00:50.767
and ate less of the things
I love.

00:50.768 --> 00:52.569
Well, let's go show you off.
Where to first?

00:52.570 --> 00:55.339
I don't know. Maybe try walking
down the stairs. Go from there.

00:55.340 --> 00:57.107
Great.

00:57.108 --> 00:59.710
Ooh! Right behind you.

00:59.711 --> 01:02.912
If my ass wasn't numb, I would
have really enjoyed that.

